Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前  被称作血腥约翰的连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害了我的妻子和女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后我们一直在追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们称之为"布莱克组织"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织里还有些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  法官  联调局探员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一个有秘密需要掩盖的执法人员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个腐败警察的秘密组织
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰是成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基拉·汀斯利死之前跟我说了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她告诉我杀她的人  也就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三个点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底谁是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们很高兴地宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于确认了他的身份与面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执法部门负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔·伯特仑局长  就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手里有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦法官的令状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局现在要关闭你们部门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了  这里没我们的事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会放弃  我不信你会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的情况我们已经无法掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持联络  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切  我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴你能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上塞车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一有空就过来见你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况真是一团糟  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听着  我觉得我们...  -一会儿有你说的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在肯定都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道接下来会发生什么事  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-探员  -所以我来说明下接下来会发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的几天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会找你们每个人谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有权委托律师或工会代表随行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你们自己选择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为何需要律师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们考虑得长远点  金宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的上司伯特仑是个罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有可能你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会非常仔细地审视你们每个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们有任何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一点点可疑的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后起诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  除非
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能够配合  那我们会非常非常满意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样你们就有点回旋的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(194.4,267.2)}加州  萨克拉门托  富兰克林区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局展开一场全球辑凶行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通缉著名的萨克拉门托执法部门官员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔·伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局方面证实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据信伯特仑就是臭名昭著的连环杀手血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他因在整个加利福尼亚州中心地带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯下一系列恐怖凶案而被通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这有公用电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里  你好啊  给我张六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一根菠萝味雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六合彩  雪茄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用不着捏着嗓子讲话  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉真奇怪啊  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们上次...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  伯特仑  还在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你问的是简  那我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去楼上找过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许还没听说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约一小时前  盖尔·伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在萨城东区的一个加油站杀了一个警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你听说了伯特仑当时在加油站做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在打公用电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜他打给了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是简
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法左右你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你的男朋友和一名危险的逃犯勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他已经深陷布莱克组织中无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是  他也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简无法阻止打给他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他也不是我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太遗憾了  特蕾莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个好警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在依旧是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们听说了伯特仑今早干的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说联调局的人在找我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在是怎样  你们就躲在停车场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是躲起来  只是潜伏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们暂时还安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少现在还没有下达对我们的逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们迟早会的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她刚已经问了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今加调局已经不复存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能靠自己了  你们得保护好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不知道简在哪里  他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想知道  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-明白  头儿  -明白  头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已经不是你们的头儿了  关键就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(400,400)\fs18\pos(191.4,278.4)}加州  萨克拉门托  威廉兰德公园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被通缉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的  艾伯特给你下了逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你到底要不要告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对  伯特仑打给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管他想说什么  他那时没时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他还在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他会很快再打来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手机不安全  联调局...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  他们装了窃听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们还没追踪到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们追踪到了  我现在就早该被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许如此  但他们早晚会追踪到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在伯特仑打来之前我不能扔掉手机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以事情就悬在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在闪烁其词
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟的眼睛圆又亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《小恐龙》[系列童书]  你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很清楚他的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  -很抱歉我那时不得不挂电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天实在太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  这个电话不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你一百美元换你的手机  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两百美元换你的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么骗局吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百美元  外加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部替代机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们  我一会儿再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交易愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚才到底说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该见面好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就我们俩  -就像约会一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得说你我确实不分伯仲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的觉得我们应该好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停战  不带武器  不玩花招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后各行其道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈谈  谈什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我们都需要结束此事了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在今天  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我时间有点紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道能否相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到现在了就别胆小了  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有那么多机会杀你  却都没下手  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  时间  地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小时后弗里蒙特公园的喷泉边见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不知道那个地方  中央汽车站见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-北入口  -不行  那里人太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且警察太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道亚历山大公墓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西门那边有个小教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊  半小时之后见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别迟到  我不能待太久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小时之后见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想见我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我知道自己在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  别去  你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局马上就要抓到伯特仑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想他落在联调局手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这一天早晚会来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我不想让你牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵扯  我早就深陷其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要借你的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  你的枪  我不会开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是壮壮胆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特蕾莎  相信我  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,疑犯逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责人呢  艾伯特在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手举到我能看见的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特在哪儿  我必须得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  淡定点  伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又不是阿尔·卡彭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}著名黑帮老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伯特  请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出来你是个正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以我的名义发誓  我一小时之内就回去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在  我...  我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别别别  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干什么  你需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回局里说怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  让她过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  里斯本女士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是咱们两个警察间帮个忙  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  我发誓到时候一定把他带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底有什么紧急的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是跟伯特仑有约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  艾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局  退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-加调局  你给我退后  -怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走  艾伯特  他什么也没做错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来不想提的  但加调局已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的警徽就是个玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你们只是在假扮警察
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你怎么说  放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是缠上我了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠上联调局了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你是真的联调局探员  有什么证据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  你们也许是布莱克组织的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是没可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出证明来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手下里德·史密斯就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们怎么知道简会不会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 艾伯特探员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在确保他的安全之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好他是我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  放下枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都放下枪  没必要起冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开我的车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让他走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了  就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你们的枪都放到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照他说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追踪里斯本探员的车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在我车上装了追踪器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不我们怎么能找到简
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过认识你们这些人我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我知道你们早晚要出篓子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能省我不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不应验了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还没准备好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我看会儿车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  会看好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  伙计  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思麻烦你了  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我长话短说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿不愿意载我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是四队  我们看见那辆车了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停在第五大道和谢尔曼街交会处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后  先退后  他们可能就在那儿接头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四队  什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四队  回答  该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿  里斯本车里就几个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简不在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发现简  重复  我们没发现简
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否收...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再越错越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是不见棺材不落泪是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  我们真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官  你居然还叫他长官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别激动  "头号公敌"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}约翰.格林杰是萧条时期联调局追捕的最著名的黑帮头目  曾两度越狱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在是阶下囚  还是识相点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  你是想住好一点的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢[西语]  奥雷利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气  祝你好运[西语]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:07.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(78,97.6)}安琪拉·萝斯金·简
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:07.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正粗倩_GBK\c&H181417&\fs12\frz-1\b1\fry5\b0\pos(316.2,99)}夏洛特·安妮·简
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先得搜搜你身上有没有武器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你才能进去  把手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.35,0:23:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试下也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么准时
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还真是俩无赖  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.87,0:24:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证  这是最后一次骗你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先说正事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和联调局犯了个严重的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.88,0:24:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.16,0:24:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉让你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我只是布莱克组织
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.20,0:24:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一员卑微走卒罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰可是高层
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.17,0:25:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是很相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信随你  但
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.60,0:25:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们草率得出的结论是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.98,0:25:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谁是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.85,0:25:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.92,0:25:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.85,0:25:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.99,0:25:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织严格遵循的原则是只须知道必需的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.26,0:25:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.73,0:25:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们完全可以在电话里说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.15,0:25:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我们在电话里说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.81,0:25:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你  你可能就不会来见我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.41,0:25:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.53,0:25:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到命令要打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.47,0:25:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你游戏结束  安排和你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.58,0:25:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.54,0:25:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.23,0:25:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你不要以为
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.65,0:25:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乐意这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.58,0:25:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织不想有遗留问题
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.96,0:25:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想留下把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.87,0:25:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.36,0:26:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手吧  奥斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.15,0:26:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别  别  听着  听着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.33,0:26:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谈谈  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.79,0:26:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  这不是我能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.01,0:26:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很喜欢你  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.59,0:26:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别  别  不需要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.89,0:26:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.39,0:26:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  奥斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.70,0:26:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以出去等着了  就...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.34,0:26:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保没人来打扰我们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.72,0:26:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.68,0:27:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.16,0:27:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯  你在干
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.71,0:27:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.38,0:27:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不如周呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.14,0:27:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们必须告诉我们到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.77,0:27:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不需要做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.75,0:27:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也什么都做不了  行行好就放松点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.09,0:27:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  我怎么放松得下来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.14,0:27:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有时候表现的好像你很享受无助感
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.89,0:27:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我收回  别放松
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.77,0:27:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用额头把车窗撞破
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.97,0:27:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就可以跳车跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.05,0:27:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计们  团结一点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.00,0:27:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.57,0:27:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"抱歉"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.60,0:27:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫林斯  你是本地人  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.04,0:27:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  林肯高地的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.31,0:27:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给我弄一张萨克拉门托的地图  -是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.07,0:27:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车里的电脑上就有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.90,0:27:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纸质地图
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.30,0:27:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纸质  地图
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:27:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点去找
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.57,0:28:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有纸质地图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.00,0:28:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  终于又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.02,0:28:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.23,0:28:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他聪明又傻
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.00,0:28:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从来没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.10,0:28:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是布莱克组织的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.27,0:28:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.47,0:28:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都认为他是血腥约翰  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.86,0:28:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们两个同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.53,0:28:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是这个故事完美的结局
